'I stayed out of trouble until about 18 months ago.'

Smith claimed Benefits Street’s cameras followed him when his life was at a 'low ebb' in his life because of a drinking problem.

He also revealed he had become a 'wanted man' and accused Benefits Street’s producers of endangering his life by implying he stole cannabis plants from a drugs gang.

Channel 4 denied his claim.

 

